{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 27960, "create_time": 1643721451, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "反过来说，只要破坏了强制义务教育和集体文化活动背后的中央集权体系，用不了两三代人，原中国大陆实现各省独立建国并不是不可想象的事。台湾就是例子。", "timestamp": 1643721451}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 27963, "create_time": 1643724599, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "我觉得洞主少考虑了一个因素，文字。东北人和广东人相隔几千公里，但书写、阅读同样的文字。这可上溯至秦始皇“书同文”，历来文化传统如此。福建人和台湾人虽仅有一海峡之隔，但文字不同，话语也不同。", "timestamp": 1643724599}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 27965, "create_time": 1643725549, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Alice: 老华人移民都是依托地域形成圈子的，比如在欧陆，东北人和浙江人是两个不同的圈子", "timestamp": 1643725549}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 27969, "create_time": 1643726165, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 3, "text": "[tmp]\nRe Alice: 欧洲人大多使用拉丁字母，可上溯至奥古斯都“书同文”，，，", "timestamp": 1643726165}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 27970, "create_time": 1643726342, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 3, "text": "[tmp]\n东北人和广州人的语言、文字、习俗差距显然很大，广州人用的一些生僻字东北人不认识，东北人用的一些生僻字广州人不认识", "timestamp": 1643726342}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 57742, "create_time": 1648086794, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "dz说的有道理，海外华人确实明显的不团结。但是就境内而言，当代的中央集权体系哪有那么容易垮台呢？那么多强大的敌对势力努力了那么多年都没成功。", "timestamp": 1648086794}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 57786, "create_time": 1648089353, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "为啥宋辽对峙